			<h4><a id="comment_link_64213302" name="comment_link_64213302" href="//linux.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23215110&amp;cid=64213302" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64213302)" >Re:   Why I don't use VS code</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64213302" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64213302); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>2</a>)</span></h4>
